628
01:13:36,520 --> 01:13:43,640
Ta la je inspirirala
ubojstvo milijuna mojih ljudi

629
01:13:43,400 --> 01:13:49,080
kroz stoljea, a ova la
inspirirala je holokaust.

630
01:13:53,960 --> 01:13:57,240
