651
01:15:54,720 --> 01:15:57,800
Nastavite traiti. Idemo.

652
01:15:57,720 --> 01:16:01,120
Pokazat u vam bombu.

653
01:16:03,760 --> 01:16:10,000
to se dogaa?
- Upalite svjetlo ovdje!

654
01:16:23,200 --> 01:16:25,080
Tony! Izlazi van!
- Nema nikakve bombe!

655
01:16:25,040 --> 01:16:27,960
